name: Datebility
overview:
Datebility.com focuses on being socially inclusive, specifically in regard to the disability community. In 1986, Datebility.com founder, Wayne Stillerman, was diagnosed with Multiple Sclerosis and 20 years later, after spending many of those on other online dating sites, sought to create a community of engaged daters who saw beyond the disability.
